h3cT1.description: This MIB provides T1 interface information that are excluded by RFC 1213 and RFC 2233

t1InterfaceStatusTable.name: t1InterfaceStatusTable
t1InterfaceStatusTable.description: This table contains interface packet statistics

t1InterfaceStatusEntry.name: t1InterfaceStatusEntry
t1InterfaceStatusEntry.description: This entry contains interface packet statistics. The index of this Entry is ifIndex defined in ifTable of RFC1213-MIB

t1InterfaceInErrs.name: t1InterfaceInErrs
t1InterfaceInErrs.description: The total number of error received on this interface

t1InterfaceInRuntsErrs.name: t1InterfaceInRuntsErrs
t1InterfaceInRuntsErrs.description: The number of Runts Error(too short packet) received on this interface

t1InterfaceInGiantsErrs.name: t1InterfaceInGiantsErrs
t1InterfaceInGiantsErrs.description: The number of Giants Error(too long packet) received on this interface

t1InterfaceInCrcErrs.name: t1InterfaceInCrcErrs
t1InterfaceInCrcErrs.description: The number of CRC Error received on this interface

t1InterfaceInAlignErrs.name: t1InterfaceInAlignErrs
t1InterfaceInAlignErrs.description: The number of Align Error received on this interface

t1InterfaceInOverRunsErrs.name: t1InterfaceInOverRunsErrs
t1InterfaceInOverRunsErrs.description: The number of Over Runs Error received on this interface

t1InterfaceInDribblesErrs.name: t1InterfaceInDribblesErrs
t1InterfaceInDribblesErrs.description: The number of dribble packets received

t1InterfaceInAbortedSeqErrs.name: t1InterfaceInAbortedSeqErrs

t1InterfaceInNoBufferErrs.name: t1InterfaceInNoBufferErrs

h3ct1Table.name: h3ct1Table
h3ct1Table.description: A list of T1 interface entries.

h3ct1Entry.name: h3ct1Entry
h3ct1Entry.description: This entry contains T1 interface management information.

H3cT1TimeSlot.name: H3cT1TimeSlot
H3cT1TimeSlot.description: Each octet within this value specifies a set of time slots, with the first octet specifying time slot 1 through 8, the second octet specifying time slots 9 through 16, etc. Within each octet, the most significant bit represents the highest numbered time slot, and the least significant bit represents the lowest numbered time slot. Thus, each time slot of the T1 is represented by a single bit within the value of this object. If that bit has a value of '1' then that time slot is included in the set of time slots; the time slot is not included if its bit has a value of '0'.

h3ct1Type.name: h3ct1Type
h3ct1Type.description: Specifies the type of the T1 interface.

h3ct1Clock.name: h3ct1Clock
h3ct1Clock.description: Specifies the clock type used on the T1 interface.

h3ct1FrameFormat.name: h3ct1FrameFormat
h3ct1FrameFormat.description: Specifies the frame format used on the T1 interface.

h3ct1LineCode.name: h3ct1LineCode
h3ct1LineCode.description: Specifies the line code type used on the T1 interface.

h3ct1PriSetTimeSlot.name: h3ct1PriSetTimeSlot
h3ct1PriSetTimeSlot.description: This is a bit-map of PRI time slots used on the T1 interface. It needs to administratively shut down the D channel of the T1 interface before cancelling PRI time slots.

h3ct1DChannelIndex.name: h3ct1DChannelIndex
h3ct1DChannelIndex.description: This is the ifIndex of the D channel of the T1 interface.

h3ct1SubScribLineChannelIndex.name: h3ct1SubScribLineChannelIndex
h3ct1SubScribLineChannelIndex.description: This is the ifIndex of the subscriber-line channel of the T1 interface.

h3ct1InterfaceTable.name: h3ct1InterfaceTable
h3ct1InterfaceTable.description: A list of channels of T1 interface entries. Including D channels and subscriber-line channels.

h3ct1InterfaceEntry.name: h3ct1InterfaceEntry
h3ct1InterfaceEntry.description: This entry contains channels of T1 interface management information. Including D channels and subscriber-line channels.

h3ct1ControllerIndex.name: h3ct1ControllerIndex
h3ct1ControllerIndex.description: Which T1 interface is this channel belonged to.
